      "title": "The emergency legislation is passed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The emergency law imposed under the Public Security Act while Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe was serving as Acting President was passed by a majority of 57 votes in the Parliament today (27th). 120 votes were received in favor of the bill and 63 votes were received against."
      ],
